snippet.textDisplay: I've had the honour of listening to Mann Saab live in 1989. His energy and intensity has been the same. Just can say one thing Proud to be A PUNJABI and if people start disliking this song then only GOD HELP THEM. Singers like Gurdas Mann, Mohd Sadiq, Narinder Biba, Amar Singh 'Chamkila', Jazzy B, Sardool Sikander, Aasa Singh, Malkit Singh, Hans Raj Hans and many many more are True Legends of Punjabi Music and SABHIYACHAR. Last but not the least the one and only USTAD NUSRAT FATEH ALI KHAN and Ustad KULDEEP MANAK
